587831,"uid":293490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"其實點解啲人成日話成個food court 好多野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a99bd4b47a41748faf18e0479daa55a036bfd76","tid":1587831,"uid":31458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:46:07.000Z","msg":"只係食鹽水雞，酸辣粉同埋皇牌冰室<br />\n其他狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794faae01d7c701660f9cd2c52439defb202b771","tid":1587831,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:49:20.000Z","msg":"樓上有間鐵板飯勁垃圾<br />\n果曰2條友去食  間鋪得2個mk仔同一個mk妹<br />\n加左可樂 拎飯果時唔記得比我<br />\n最仆街係 我fd叫左個咖哩鐵板飯<br />\n拎到返黎個飯完全係白色 即刻返去同佢再嘈過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地收返個飯走係廚房對住碟飯係咁笑同吹水<br />\n望撚住佢地成分鐘先出黎同我講 佢地既咖哩係特別d 好似係粉黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係當我地on9 成碟飯1粒咖哩粉都無 唔記得加咪認撚左佢lor<br />\n之後叫佢再做過 個樣先似返menu個圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 上年食  唔知仲係唔係到"},{"pid":"b5386729318bc3e3a892723e914c5b166cf0f791","tid":1587831,"uid":161037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:00:03.000Z","msg":"我嗰個係咪垃圾胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓下嘅話我覺得米線同鹽水雞唔錯<br />\n樓上除咗冰室都不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672a7bba8311e64f2774656281e47c3e25eb4ca2","tid":1587831,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:11:15.000Z","msg":"基本上樓上全部垃圾黎，得d mk做侍應<br />\n<br />\n下面台灣野同泰國野還可以"},{"pid":"6fb9db6f8235bf10c85d0b3e65bf7676ce840a29","tid":1587831,"uid":276401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾胃二號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得樓上意粉好食喎~<br />\n<br />\n不過邊爐真心衰<br />\n味道就中下啦<br />\n不過DLLM成百蚊俾成獲芽菜好PK<br />\n仲有個獲真係好L污糟<br />\n請我都唔會再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}